<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ca">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Confirmació de reserva – Correllengua</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#f6f1e7;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">

  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#f6f1e7;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding:40px 16px;">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="max-width:520px;">

          <!-- Red header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#cf2e27;border-radius:12px 12px 0 0;padding:24px 32px;text-align:center;">
              <img src="https://correllenguaagermanat.cat/assets/logo-correllengua-blanc-lletres-C2OZgadl.png"
                   alt="Correllengua" width="420" height="120"
                   style="display:block;margin:0 auto;border:0;max-width:100%;" />
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Body -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color:#f6f3ea;border:1px solid rgba(29,29,27,0.12);border-top:none;border-radius:0 0 12px 12px;padding:32px;">

              <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:18px;color:#1d1d1b;">
                Hola <strong>{{ participant.name }} {{ participant.surname }}</strong>,
              </p>
              <p style="margin:0 0 24px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#555550;line-height:1.6;">
                La teva inscripció al Correllengua ha quedat confirmada. A continuació trobaràs el resum de les teves reserves.
              </p>

              {% for segment in segments %}
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid rgba(29,29,27,0.12);border-radius:8px;margin-bottom:16px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:20px;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Recorregut: <strong style="color:#1d1d1b;">{{ segment.routeName|default('–') }}</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Hora: <strong style="color:#1d1d1b;">{{ segment.time|default('–') }}</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Itinerari: <strong style="color:#1d1d1b;">{{ segment.itinerary|default('–') }}</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Tram: <strong style="color:#1d1d1b;">{{ segment.position|default('–') }}</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 6px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Modalitat: <strong style="color:#1d1d1b;">{{ segment.modality|default('–') }}</strong></p>
                    <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888882;">Punt de sortida: <a href="{{ segment.mapLink }}" style="color:#cf2e27;text-decoration:underline;font-weight:bold;">Veure al mapa</a></p>
                    <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="border-radius:999px;border:1.5px solid #cf2e27;">
                          <a href="{{ segment.deregisterLink }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:8px 16px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;color:#cf2e27;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;line-height:1;">
                            Cancel·lar aquest tram
                          </a>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              {% endfor %}

              {% if segments|length > 1 %}
              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="border-radius:999px;background-color:#cf2e27;">
                    <a href="{{ deregisterAllLink }}" style="display:inline-block;padding:10px 20px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;line-height:1;">
                      Cancel·lar totes les reserves
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              {% endif %}

              <hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(29,29,27,0.12);margin:24px 0;" />

              <p style="margin:0 0 8px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1d1d1b;line-height:1.6;">
                Si per qualsevol motiu necessites cancel·lar alguna de les teves participacions, pots fer-ho des dels botons anteriors. Guarda aquest correu per poder accedir als teus enllaços de cancel·lació.
              </p>

              <p style="margin:24px 0 4px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1d1d1b;">Fins aviat!</p>
              <p style="margin:0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1d1d1b;">
                <strong>Correllengua Agermanat</strong>
              </p>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- CTA links -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px 0 0;text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 12px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#555550;">Vols col·laborar més amb el Correllengua?</p>
              <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" style="margin:0 auto;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding-right:10px;">
                    <a href="https://correllenguaagermanat.cat/donatiu"
                       style="display:inline-block;padding:9px 20px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#f6f3ea;background-color:#cf2e27;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;line-height:1;">
                      Fes un donatiu
                    </a>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <a href="https://correllenguaagermanat.cat/botigues"
                       style="display:inline-block;padding:9px 20px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#cf2e27;border:1.5px solid #cf2e27;text-decoration:none;border-radius:999px;line-height:1;">
                      Compra samarretes
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:20px 0 0;text-align:center;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:11px;color:#aaaaaa;">
                Correllengua Agermanat · <a href="https://correllenguaagermanat.cat" style="color:#cf2e27;text-decoration:none;">correllenguaagermanat.cat</a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
